cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DL 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and text classification. The use of neural networks and deep reinforcement learning also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the use of reinforcement learning specifically suggests that it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the use of deep learning techniques such as neural network representation of sentences suggests that it could belong to cs.DL (Deep Learning).
